Class POMergeJoin.TuplesToSchemaTupleList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pig.backend.hadoop.executionengine.physicalLayer.relationalOperators.POMergeJoin.TuplesToSchemaTupleList
  • Enclosing class:
    POMergeJoin

    public static class POMergeJoin.TuplesToSchemaTupleList
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class that extends ArrayList, making it easy to provide on the fly conversion from Tuple to SchemaTuple. This is necessary because we are not getting SchemaTuples from the source, though in the future that is what we would like to do.
